      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-spec example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with precision. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear torque and that signature metallic rasp. A true analog performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
